{"tid":2398336,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"(無人講我講囉\\無人玩我玩囉)狼人之末日怒吼：地靈之血","createTime":"2021-02-07T08:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T08:10:17.000Z","uid":173561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"331071445aac867953383421449c30e716672646","tid":2398336,"uid":173561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T08:10:17.000Z","msg":"早幾日行下睇下有咩game好玩就發現左哩隻啦,300都唔駛仲要有中文添.所以就想推薦俾大家.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/URY86LE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURY86LE.jpg&h=908d9733&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>隻game有中文嘅,但可能少亞洲人玩所以片/圖係英文</strong><br />\n<br />\n大嘅就係主角係一個狼人部族嘅戰士,佢就要同佢嘅盟友同埋部族成員一齊抵抗企圖破壞佢地聖地/大自然嘅企業嘅故事<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LuBR4xA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLuBR4xA.jpg&h=aaf7d1e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p8hxOZf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp8hxOZf.jpg&h=165dae66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主要潛行多，不過你殺意起可以隨時變身(除非講明唔可以被人發現)，AI唔算聰明同埋巡邏路線都唔算複雜，睇多幾次就過到。不過講時機就真，如果miss 左嘅load save/直接開打好過。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=28HvGmg-Jqg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D28HvGmg-Jqg&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOZdwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=f607aeeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=28HvGmg-Jqg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HxQyLXFRc6U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHxQyLXFRc6U&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOZdwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=ea48d3a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HxQyLXFRc6U</a><br />\n<br />\ngame 入面有一個簡單嘅技能樹可以俾玩家學技,從潛行到戰鬥都有.執精靈或者係做任會填充一項名為精靈點嘅bar,填滿就會有技能<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ke4XfEv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fke4XfEv.jpg&h=7216f223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隻game有兩個唔太好地方:<br />\n<br />\n第一係畫質偏低. 個人推斷最多係720島,當係低質版復仇者聯盟咁睇.<br />\n<br />\n第二係略嫌唔夠血腥,雖則係行暴力風但竟然無斷肢/分屍之類場面出現只係搞到成地血就算哩度扣左分.<br />\n<br />\n推薦大家玩normal先,跟住如果嫌太易打想要D挑戰先再轉hard都未遲(可以中途轉)"}]}